flowchart TD
    START([START]) --> self_awareness
    self_awareness --> search_planner
    search_planner -->|queries empty| web_search
    search_planner -->|cursor >= N| clarify_with_user
    web_search --> search_planner
    clarify_with_user -->|interrupt + resume| outline_generator
    outline_generator --> chapter_guard
    chapter_guard -->|pending chapter| write_lesson
    chapter_guard -->|all done| END([END])
    write_lesson -->|lesson_pos > lpc| activities_generator
    write_lesson --> critic_node
    critic_node -->|passes| accept_lesson
    critic_node -->|fails| reject_lesson
    accept_lesson --> activities_generator
    reject_lesson -->|attempt<3| write_lesson
    reject_lesson -->|attempt>=3 force-accept| chapter_guard
    activities_generator -->|more plans ready| activities_generator
    activities_generator -->|none ready| chapter_guard
